This is my custom initrd files for Ubuntu Touch.

Two scripts are in this directory:
 -> dec: decompress the boot.img ramdisk (boot.img-ramdisk) and kernel (boot.img-kernel.gz)
 -> rep: move the old boot.img into boot.old, compress boot.img-ramdisk and boot.img-kernel.gz into a brand-new boot.img, remove temp files and boot the boot.img via fastboot.
